    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pincers with broad flat jaws used for applying pressure to bands during the book covering process, especially for nipping up.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
